sage is actually directed at me or if 张玲 is asking me to look into something. The referenced message about confirming today's \"偏均衡/进攻\"口径 doesn't appear to be from me based on the conversation flow, so I should probably just ask for clarification about what specifically needs to be investigated.","thinkingSignature":"d5cbceffadd1c633376db209ace3cd38cdde01900d2a5ca6718edd54479c6390"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n这条消息看起来是在问之前关于\"偏均衡/进攻\"口径的确认结果——但那是您说要自己先去确认的事情，我没有这段上下文。\n\n如果您已经确认完了，可以告诉我结论，我来记录或做相应处理。\n\n---\n\n另外，**当前我的主任务是扫码登录修复**（见上方 ACTIVE_TASK），正在进行根因排查，尚未完成。如果您有其他优先级指示，请告诉我。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85,"output":556,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":626,"totalTokens":26144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773970819278}}
