{"type":"message","id":"9ad5f832","parentId":"1ed1be00","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:55:59.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The index CSV files only go through 20260319 (yesterday). The data is stale. On today (20260320), the script is using 20260319's return as if it were today's return.\n\nSo the `-2.31%` is yesterday's (2026-03-19) 中证2000 (ZZ2000) return, which is from yesterday's close. But the system is treating it as today's market condition for the halt gate.\n\nThis is a data freshness bug - the gate should check whether the latest data is actually from today before applying it. Or it should use yesterday's data explicitly labeled as such.\n\n\nThe gate is mislabeling yesterday's market move as today's, which is why it's triggering a halt when the actual market is up today. I need to report this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"03a0cd127f065ce41558e9f22a29578bfebf236c2694b32345d5680674df4675"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n找到原因了——这是个**数据陈旧 bug**，不是今日数据。\n\n**实际来源**：`index_000852_SH.csv`（中证2000）的最后一条记录是：\n\n```\n000852.SH, 20260319, 7909.23, -2.3141%\n```\n\n也就是 **2026-03-19（昨天）** 的收盘数据。系统把它当成今天的数据灌进了风控门控，导致误判。\n\n**结论**：\n- `-2.31%` = 昨天（周四）的中证2000跌幅，是历史数据，不是今天的实时/盘中数据\n- 今天（周五，是交易日）A股实际是涨的，但门控系统读取的是昨天数据\n\n**这是数据管道的 bug**：今天（03-20交易日）没有新的指数数据写入 CSV，所以 `latest_index_return_pct()` 拿到的是昨天数据。\n\n需要我查一下今早的数据抓取为什么没有更新到今天的文件吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48545,"output":374,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773971746341}}
