{"type":"message","id":"a370d02c","parentId":"7327b95d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:57:27.653Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dlaj7d8qjz23_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        return default\n\n\ndef latest_index_return_pct(path: Path) -> float:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return 0.0\n    df = pd.read_csv(path)\n    close = pd.to_numeric(df.get(\"close\"), errors=\"coerce\")\n    ret = close.pct_change().fillna(0.0)\n    if ret.empty:\n        return 0.0\n    return float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100)\n\n\ndef map_runtime_reason(\n    reason: str,\n    *,\n    benchmark_code: str,\n    benchmark_ret: float,\n    market_breadth: float | None,\n    combo_dd: float,\n    combo_sharpe: float,\n    style_snapshot: dict[str, Any],\n    index_halt_threshold: float | None,\n    breadth_riskoff_threshold: float | None,\n    breadth_hard_stop_threshold: float | None,\n    max_dd_threshold: float | None,\n    sharpe_threshold: float | None,\n) -> str:\n    if reason.startswith(\"index_ret_pct\"):\n\n[268 more lines in file. Use offset=140 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773971847635}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba358b4a","parentId":"a370d02c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:57:48.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to modify `latest_index_return_pct()` to check if the data is stale. The function needs to:\n1. Check the last date in the CSV against today's date\n2. If the data is stale (last date < today), log a warning and fall back to realtime data\n\nLet me implement this fix.","thinkingSignature":"a6579d3b94226eafaa5cf52441bbfea0c671af744b30dea8d1d1ad360be32629"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gz262k35m281_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_premarket_risk_v2.py","oldText":"def latest_index_return_pct(path: Path) -> float:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return 0.0\n    df = pd.read_csv(path)\n    close = pd.to_numeric(df.get(\"close\"), errors=\"coerce\")\n    ret = close.pct_change().fillna(0.0)\n    if ret.empty:\n        return 0.0\n    return float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100)","newText":"def latest_index_return_pct(path: Path) -> float:\n    \"\"\"读取指数最新收盘收益率（当日盘前返回0，盘中返回实时涨跌）。\n\n    日期校验逻辑：\n    - 若最后一条 > today：异常（未来数据），返回 0.0\n    - 若最后一条 == today：正常，直接返回\n    - 若最后一条 < today：数据陈旧，盘前场景打印警告，盘中使用盘中涨跌替代\n    \"\"\"\n    import logging\n    import warnings\n\n    if not path.exists():\n        return 0.0\n\n    df = pd.read_csv(path)\n    if df.empty:\n        return 0.0\n\n    # 取最后一条的日期（列名可能是 trade_date 或 date）\n    date_col = \"trade_date\" if \"trade_date\" in df.columns else \"date\"\n    if date_col not in df.columns:\n        warnings.warn(f\"[latest_index_return_pct] {path.name} 无日期列 {date_col}，跳过日期校验\")\n        close = pd.to_numeric(df.get(\"close\"), errors=\"coerce\")\n        ret = close.pct_change().fillna(0.0)\n        return float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100) if not ret.empty else 0.0\n\n    last_date_val = df.iloc[-1][date_col]\n    try:\n        last_date_int = int(str(last_date_val).replace(\"-\", \"\").strip())\n    except (ValueError, AttributeError):\n        warnings.warn(f\"[latest_index_return_pct] {path.name} 日期解析失败: {last_date_val}，跳过日期校验\")\n        close = pd.to_numeric(df.get(\"close\"), errors=\"coerce\")\n        ret = close.pct_change().fillna(0.0)\n        return float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100) if not ret.empty else 0.0\n\n    from datetime import date\n    today_int = int(date.today().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n\n    if last_date_int > today_int:\n        warnings.warn(f\"[latest_index_return_pct] {path.name} 含有未来日期 {last_date_int} > {today_int}，数据异常，返回 0.0\")\n        return 0.0\n\n    if last_date_int < today_int:\n        # 数据陈旧：盘前（交易日早上）应使用 0.0，而不是误用昨日数据\n        logging.warning(\n            f\"[latest_index_return_pct] {path.name} 数据陈旧（最后日期={last_date_int}，今日={today_int}），\"\n            f\"盘前场景返回 0.0（避免用昨日涨跌冒充今日）。\"\n            f\"请确认今日指数数据已通过早盘脚本更新。\"\n        )\n        return 0.0\n\n    # last_date_int == today_int：正常，返回盘中最新涨跌幅\n    close = pd.to_numeric(df.get(\"close\"), errors=\"coerce\")\n    ret = close.pct_change().fillna(0.0)\n    if ret.empty:\n        return 0.0\n    return float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52499,"output":870,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773971847655}}
