{"type":"message","id":"1cc82ed0","parentId":"1aee87b1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:58:09.574Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ltzucf1cu9pd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"dd_target = parse_float(target_cfg.get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot(config)\n\n    benchmark_code = str(constraints_cfg.get(\"benchmark_smallcap\", \"ZZ2000\"))\n    benchmark_ret = parse_float(index_ret.get(benchmark_code), parse_float(index_ret.get(\"ZZ2000\"), 0.0))\n\n    runtime_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=dd_target)\n    decision = RiskEngine(runtime_cfg).evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=benchmark_ret,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=combo_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=combo_sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\") is not None else None,\n        )\n    )\n\n    reasons = [\n        map_runtime_reason(\n            item,\n            benchmark_code=benchmark_code,\n            benchmark_ret=benchmark_ret,\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            combo_dd=combo_dd,\n            combo_sharpe=combo_sharpe,\n            style_snapshot=style_snapshot,\n            index_halt_threshold=runtime_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct,\n            breadth_riskoff_threshold=runtime_cfg.market_breadth_riskoff_threshold,\n            breadth_hard_stop_threshold=runtime_cfg.market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold,\n            max_dd_threshold=runtime_cfg.strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct,\n            sharpe_threshold=runtime_cfg.strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold,\n        )\n        for item in decision.reasons\n    ]\n\n    score = 0\n    if decision.hard_stop:\n        score += 4\n    elif decision.risk_off:\n        score += 3\n    elif decision.mode == \"cautious\":\n        score += 2\n    score += min(2, max(0, len(decision.reasons) - 1))\n\n    if decision.hard_stop:\n        level = \"RED\"\n        gross_scale = 0.3\n    elif decision.risk_off:\n        level = \"YELLOW\"\n        gross_scale = 0.6\n    elif decision.mode == \"cautious\":\n        level = \"YELLOW\"\n        gross_scale = 0.8\n    else:\n        level = \"GREEN\"\n        gross_scale = 1.0\n\n    return {\n        \"score\": score,\n        \"level\": level,\n        \"mode\": decision.mode,\n        \"halt_new_buy\": decision.halt_new_buy,\n        \"risk_off\": decision.risk_off,\n        \"hard_stop\": decision.hard_stop,\n        \"gross_scale\": gross_scale,\n        \"reasons\": reasons,\n        \"raw_reasons\": decision.reasons,\n        \"market_breadth\": market_breadth,\n        \"style_snapshot\": style_snapshot,\n        \"runtime_gate\": {\n            \"benchmark_code\": benchmark_code,\n            \"benchmark_ret_pct\": round(benchmark_ret, 4),\n            \"index_halt_threshold_pct\": runtime_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"dd_target = parse_float(target_cfg.get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot(config)\n\n    benchmark_code = str(constraints_cfg.get(\"benchmark_smallcap\", \"ZZ2000\"))\n    benchmark_ret = parse_float(index_ret.get(benchmark_code), parse_float(index_ret.get(\"ZZ2000\"), 0.0))\n\n    runtime_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=dd_target)\n    decision = RiskEngine(runtime_cfg).evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=benchmark_ret,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=combo_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=combo_sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\") is not None else None,\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\"), 0.0)\n            if style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\") is not None else None,\n        )\n    )\n\n    reasons = [\n        map_runtime_reason(\n            item,\n            benchmark_code=benchmark_code,\n            benchmark_ret=benchmark_ret,\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            combo_dd=combo_dd,\n            combo_sharpe=combo_sharpe,\n            style_snapshot=style_snapshot,\n            index_halt_threshold=runtime_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct,\n            breadth_riskoff_threshold=runtime_cfg.market_breadth_riskoff_threshold,\n            breadth_hard_stop_threshold=runtime_cfg.market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold,\n            max_dd_threshold=runtime_cfg.strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct,\n            sharpe_threshold=runtime_cfg.strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold,\n        )\n        for item in decision.reasons\n    ]\n\n    score = 0\n    if decision.hard_stop:\n        score += 4\n    elif decision.risk_off:\n        score += 3\n    elif decision.mode == \"cautious\":\n        score += 2\n    score += min(2, max(0, len(decision.reasons) - 1))\n\n    if decision.hard_stop:\n        level = \"RED\"\n        gross_scale = 0.3\n    elif decision.risk_off:\n        level = \"YELLOW\"\n        gross_scale = 0.6\n    elif decision.mode == \"cautious\":\n        level = \"YELLOW\"\n        gross_scale = 0.8\n    else:\n        level = \"GREEN\"\n        gross_scale = 1.0\n\n    return {\n        \"score\": score,\n        \"level\": level,\n        \"mode\": decision.mode,\n        \"halt_new_buy\": decision.halt_new_buy,\n        \"risk_off\": decision.risk_off,\n        \"hard_stop\": decision.hard_stop,\n        \"gross_scale\": gross_scale,\n        \"reasons\": reasons,\n        \"raw_reasons\": decision.reasons,\n        \"market_breadth\": market_breadth,\n        \"style_snapshot\": style_snapshot,\n        \"runtime_gate\": {\n            \"benchmark_code\": benchmark_code,\n            \"benchmark_ret_pct\": round(benchmark_ret, 4),\n            \"index_halt_threshold_pct\": runtime_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct,","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773971889560}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dec2e99","parentId":"1cc82ed0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:58:18.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full flow. The `evaluate_risk` function takes `index_ret` (a dict of index returns) and uses `benchmark_ret` as the `index_ret_pct` for the `RiskContext`. \n\nThe fix I already made (`latest_index_return_pct` returning 0.0 when data is stale) means that `benchmark_ret` will now be 0.0 in the morning when data is stale, instead of yesterday's -2.31%.\n\nThis is much better - with benchmark_ret = 0.0 and index_halt_threshold = -1.5%, the condition `benchmark_ret <= index_halt_threshold` (i.e., 0.0 <= -1.5%) is False, so the index hard stop won't trigger.\n \nI should verify this fix works end-to-end and make sure the warning message itself is informative enough for users to understand what's happening. The fix is already done, so let me test the full morning scan pipeline to verify everything works correctly with the corrected index return values.","thinkingSignature":"69794ed6a20f0b6384db88a649f77377bf57e5ee4757ff0086bc65f43a5d983c"},{"type":"text","text":"修复已验证生效。现在完整跑一下盘前预检，验证风控门控不再用昨天的 -2.31%：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b1dfw6bmumsl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000 2>&1 | tail -30","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55712,"output":341,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773971889577}}
