{"type":"message","id":"b4ad0b0b","parentId":"a5962c98","timestamp":"2026-03-20T01:58:47.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue clearly:\n- `zz2000_ret_pct：-2.31%` - This is yesterday's return being used as if it's today's\n- The brief was generated at 09:58 this morning, using yesterday's data\n\nThe fix I made will prevent this in future runs. But I also need to ensure the morning index data fetch happens. Let me now report the findings and the fix clearly.\n\nBut first, let me also check if there's a way to force refresh today's data. The problem is that today's data can only be obtained AFTER the market closes (end-of-day data). So in the morning, the most recent data available is from yesterday.\n\n\nThis reveals two distinct problems: the stale data check I already fixed prevents old data from being misread as current, but there's also no mechanism to pull fresh index data on trading days before the market opens. I should look into what AkShare offers for real-time index quotes that could update throughout the day.","thinkingSignature":"65d8ea0866ca5ec27f69cbde5ab6972277308d36bf48fc3e0d9fbb0a6236898a"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n找到完整的根因链：\n\n**问题 1（已修复）**：`latest_index_return_pct()` 无视数据日期，直接取最后一条。昨天 18:10 更新后，今早 09:00 读取的仍是 03-19 的 -2.31%，被当成今日指数收益灌进门控。\n\n**修复**：加入日期校验，数据陈旧时打印警告并返回 0.0，而不是误用昨日数据。\n```\n# 修复前\nreturn float(ret.iloc[-1] * 100)  # 直接取最后一条，不问日期\n\n# 修复后\nif last_date_int < today_int:\n    logging.warning(\"数据陈旧（最后日期=20260319，今日=20260320），盘前场景返回 0.0\")\n    return 0.0\n```\n\n**问题 2**（需要补充）：早晨没有更新指数 CSV 的步骤。`fetch_data.py` 只在每天收盘后（18:10）运行一次，所以今早的 CSV 里没有今天的指数数据。\n\n今早生成的报告里出现了 `-2.31%` 就是因为这个——系统用了昨天的收盘数据冒充今天。\n\n**后续建议**（需要你确认是否要做）：\n- 方案 A：在 `morning_scan.py` 里加一个 AkShare 实时指数行情（不需要等收盘），盘前把实时涨跌刷进门控（覆盖昨天的收盘涨跌）\n- 方案 B：盘前门控完全不做指数收益拦截，改用市场宽度作为主要门控指标\n\n需要我执行哪个方案？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57747,"output":527,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773971911426}}
