{"type":"message","id":"dd21972a","parentId":"a288c49e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:04:21.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qm0cektiaz76_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def load_index_return_pct_for_date(\n    date_tag: str,\n    benchmark_code: str = \"ZZ2000\",\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> float:\n    normalized_code = str(benchmark_code or \"ZZ2000\").strip().upper() or \"ZZ2000\"\n    index_path = resolve_index_file(normalized_code, index_file_map=index_file_map)\n    if index_path is None:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指数文件: {normalized_code}\")\n\n    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n    frame = load_index_close_frame(index_path)\n    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n    if frame.empty:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"指数 {normalized_code} 在 {date_tag} 之前无可用数据: {index_path}\")\n    if len(frame) < 2:\n        return 0.0\n\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    prev_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-2][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or prev_close <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return round((latest_close / prev_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)\n\n\ndef _window_return_pct(frame: pd.DataFrame, window: int) -> float | None:\n    if window <= 0 or len(frame) <= window:\n        return None\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    base_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1 - window][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or base_close <= 0:\n        return None\n    return round((latest_close / base_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)\n\n\ndef load_style_rotation_snapshot_for_date(\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    date_tag: str,\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    style_cfg = resolve_style_rotation_config(config)\n    snapshot: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": bool(style_cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)),\n        \"smallcap_index\": style_cfg.get(\"smallcap_index\", \"ZZ2000\"),\n        \"broad_index\": style_cfg.get(\"broad_index\", \"HS300\"),\n        \"short_window\": int(style_cfg.get(\"short_window\", 5)),"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"def load_index_return_pct_for_date(\n    date_tag: str,\n    benchmark_code: str = \"ZZ2000\",\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> float:\n    normalized_code = str(benchmark_code or \"ZZ2000\").strip().upper() or \"ZZ2000\"\n    index_path = resolve_index_file(normalized_code, index_file_map=index_file_map)\n    if index_path is None:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指数文件: {normalized_code}\")\n\n    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n    frame = load_index_close_frame(index_path)\n    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n    if frame.empty:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"指数 {normalized_code} 在 {date_tag} 之前无可用数据: {index_path}\")\n    if len(frame) < 2:\n        return 0.0\n\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    prev_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-2][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or prev_close <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return round((latest_close / prev_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)\n\n\ndef _window_return_pct(frame: pd.DataFrame, window: int) -> float | None:\n    if window <= 0 or len(frame) <= window:\n        return None\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    base_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1 - window][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or base_close <= 0:\n        return None\n    return round((latest_close / base_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)\n\n\ndef load_style_rotation_snapshot_for_date(\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    date_tag: str,\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    style_cfg = resolve_style_rotation_config(config)\n    snapshot: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": bool(style_cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)),\n        \"smallcap_index\": style_cfg.get(\"smallcap_index\", \"ZZ2000\"),\n        \"broad_index\": style_cfg.get(\"broad_index\", \"HS300\"),\n        \"short_window\": int(style_cfg.get(\"short_window\", 5)),","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773972261688}}
{"type":"message","id":"114f4583","parentId":"dd21972a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:04:32.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue! `load_index_return_pct_for_date()` takes a `date_tag` (e.g., \"20260320\") and uses it as a cutoff: `frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key]`. It then takes the LATEST available data that's <= the cutoff date. So for date_tag=20260320, it would take the last row with date_key <= 20260320, which would be 20260319 (yesterday's close). And it calculates `latest_close / prev_close - 1` = today's close (20260319) / yesterday's close (20260318) - 1 = -2.31%.\n\nThis function has NO date freshness check. It just takes whatever is the last available data on or before the given date. \n\nSo when `run_intraday_risk_recheck.py` calls this with today's date, it retrieves yesterday's data, and the fix I made to `latest_index_return_pct()` in `run_premarket_risk_v2.py` doesn't actually help since `runtime_date_utils.py` is a separate module with its own implementation. I need to apply the same date freshness validation to `load_index_return_pct_for_date()` as well.","thinkingSignature":"1993836e15d4c5ca2edabd9e9e8a6e1364467a191e5a203631438922b5faefb2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ez7gn2jqxokr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '1,30p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/runtime_date_utils.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69406,"output":325,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773972261701}}
