{"type":"message","id":"61365111","parentId":"35c4a4d6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:04:46.118Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r3m7u4pst4on_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"42:def date_tag_to_key(value: Any) -> int:\n84:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n91:    frame = frame[frame[\"trade_date\"].astype(int) <= cutoff_key].copy()\n129:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n131:    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n175:        \"requested_date_key\": date_tag_to_key(date_tag),\n176:        \"source_date_key\": None,\n192:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n195:    smallcap_frame = smallcap_frame[smallcap_frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n196:    broad_frame = broad_frame[broad_frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"42:def date_tag_to_key(value: Any) -> int:\n84:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n91:    frame = frame[frame[\"trade_date\"].astype(int) <= cutoff_key].copy()\n129:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n131:    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n175:        \"requested_date_key\": date_tag_to_key(date_tag),\n176:        \"source_date_key\": None,\n192:    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n195:    smallcap_frame = smallcap_frame[smallcap_frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n196:    broad_frame = broad_frame[broad_frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773972286103}}
{"type":"message","id":"db0181d2","parentId":"61365111","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:05:14.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - `date_key` is an integer format like `20260320`. Now let me add a freshness check to `load_index_return_pct_for_date`. The logic:\n\n1. After getting `frame`, check if the latest date is from today\n2. If latest date < today: we have stale data → return 0.0 with warning\n3. If latest date == today: return the computed return (this is after market close, daily bar is available)","thinkingSignature":"51468ee19e39a5ff0efb012ac1014606195026497c4126eab0003301e9f1f795"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1eu4sgpjyi0c_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/runtime_date_utils.py","oldText":"def load_index_return_pct_for_date(\n    date_tag: str,\n    benchmark_code: str = \"ZZ2000\",\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> float:\n    normalized_code = str(benchmark_code or \"ZZ2000\").strip().upper() or \"ZZ2000\"\n    index_path = resolve_index_file(normalized_code, index_file_map=index_file_map)\n    if index_path is None:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指数文件: {normalized_code}\")\n\n    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n    frame = load_index_close_frame(index_path)\n    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n    if frame.empty:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"指数 {normalized_code} 在 {date_tag} 之前无可用数据: {index_path}\")\n    if len(frame) < 2:\n        return 0.0\n\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    prev_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-2][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or prev_close <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return round((latest_close / prev_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)","newText":"def load_index_return_pct_for_date(\n    date_tag: str,\n    benchmark_code: str = \"ZZ2000\",\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> float:\n    \"\"\"加载指定日期的指数收益率。\n\n    日期新鲜度校验：\n    - 若最新数据日期 < today（数据陈旧）：打印警告并返回 0.0，\n      防止把昨日收盘涨跌误当作今日盘中涨跌用于门控判断。\n    - 若最新数据日期 == today：正常返回当日涨跌幅。\n    - 若最新数据日期 > today：异常（未来数据），返回 0.0。\n    \"\"\"\n    import logging\n    import warnings\n\n    normalized_code = str(benchmark_code or \"ZZ2000\").strip().upper() or \"ZZ2000\"\n    index_path = resolve_index_file(normalized_code, index_file_map=index_file_map)\n    if index_path is None:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指数文件: {normalized_code}\")\n\n    cutoff_key = date_tag_to_key(date_tag)\n    frame = load_index_close_frame(index_path)\n    frame = frame[frame[\"date_key\"] <= cutoff_key].copy()\n    if frame.empty:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"指数 {normalized_code} 在 {date_tag} 之前无可用数据: {index_path}\")\n    if len(frame) < 2:\n        return 0.0\n\n    # 日期新鲜度检查（防止用昨日数据冒充今日盘中涨跌）\n    latest_date_key = int(frame.iloc[-1][\"date_key\"])\n    from datetime import date\n    today_key = int(date.today().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n\n    if latest_date_key > today_key:\n        warnings.warn(\n            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] {normalized_code} 含未来日期 {latest_date_key} > {today_key}，\"\n            f\"数据异常，返回 0.0\"\n        )\n        return 0.0\n\n    if latest_date_key < today_key:\n        # 数据陈旧：昨日收盘数据在今早被误用。\n        # 盘前（09:25 前）应返回 0.0；盘中若有实时数据源应优先使用。\n        logging.warning(\n            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] {normalized_code} 数据陈旧（最后日期={latest_date_key}，\"\n            f\"今日={today_key}），返回 0.0 而非昨日涨跌。\"\n            f\"如需盘中实时涨跌，需在 morning_scan 中更新实时指数数据。\"\n        )\n        return 0.0\n\n    # latest_date_key == today_key：正常，当日日线已就绪\n    latest_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-1][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    prev_close = parse_float(frame.iloc[-2][\"close\"], 0.0)\n    if latest_close <= 0 or prev_close <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return round((latest_close / prev_close - 1.0) * 100.0, 4)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":70754,"output":1087,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773972286120}}
