{"type":"message","id":"e7f6b9cb","parentId":"841583c0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:05:57.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The daily index data only has data up to 03-19. There's no way to get today's intraday data using `stock_zh_index_daily` since that only provides end-of-day data.\n\nFor the morning scan to update the index data with today's return, we would need to either:\n1. Wait until after market close (15:00) for the daily bar to be written\n2. Use a real-time API (which was flaky earlier)\n\nThe practical approach for Option A is to write a morning_scan step that:\n1. Checks if the CSV was updated today (mtime check)2. If not updated today (stale), try to get real-time data from AkShare or pytdx\n\n\n3. If real-time fails, update the CSV with a \"last updated\" timestamp so downstream functions know the data is stale\n\nActually, the cleanest approach given the constraints: I should just focus on the key fix I've already done (date validation in both functions) which prevents the wrong data from being used. For the real-time index update in morning_scan, I'll add a step that tries to get real-time data, and if successful, writes it to the CSV. But given the network flakiness, a more robust approach would be to just update the mtime of the CSV when morning_scan runs.\n\nWait, I'm overcomplicating this. The date validation is already handling the stale data issue - it returns 0.0 when the data isn't from today. So for a pre-market gate check, returning 0.0 is actually the right behavior since we don't have today's data yet. The gate shouldn't trigger a halt based on yesterday's data. The real solution is to add real-time index fetching to morning_scan.py so today's intraday data gets captured and used for the gate check instead of falling back to stale data.\n\nI'll add a function that fetches current index prices and calculates returns against yesterday's close, then writes the results to a JSON file that the gate can use.","thinkingSignature":"cf27b78c0ba8ff2a70825062cdd8503d948a42616ef5cc033bf580ef8a36cb82"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mhjjl1xa6021_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":30,"limit":20,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/morning_scan.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72721,"output":467,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773972341237}}
