{"type":"message","id":"d1f9014d","parentId":"b7fe9a51","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:06:49.022Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zeq1glk2mzm9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def load_index_return_pct_for_date(\n    date_tag: str,\n    benchmark_code: str = \"ZZ2000\",\n    *,\n    index_file_map: dict[str, Path] | None = None,\n) -> float:\n    \"\"\"加载指定日期的指数收益率。\n\n    日期新鲜度校验：\n    - 若最新数据日期 < today（数据陈旧）：打印警告并返回 0.0，\n      防止把昨日收盘涨跌误当作今日盘中涨跌用于门控判断。\n    - 若最新数据日期 == today：正常返回当日涨跌幅。\n    - 若最新数据日期 > today：异常（未来数据），返回 0.0。\n    \"\"\"\n    import logging\n\n[200 more lines in file. Use offset=133 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773972409009}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fd277de","parentId":"d1f9014d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:07:02.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to add a fallback to read from the realtime JSON when the CSV data is stale. Let me update the part after the logging warning to try the realtime JSON first before returning 0.0:","thinkingSignature":"ad3f90f0fe86c280859682164b92b32a770e56d45d396cd36e7867945009f841"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ocpmuni8mxa5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/runtime_date_utils.py","oldText":"    if latest_date_key < today_key:\n        # 数据陈旧：昨日收盘数据在今早被误用。\n        # 盘前（09:25 前）应返回 0.0；盘中若有实时数据源应优先使用。\n        logging.warning(\n            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] {normalized_code} 数据陈旧（最后日期={latest_date_key}，\"\n            f\"今日={today_key}），返回 0.0 而非昨日涨跌。\"\n            f\"如需盘中实时涨跌，需在 morning_scan 中更新实时指数数据。\"\n        )\n        return 0.0","newText":"    if latest_date_key < today_key:\n        # 数据陈旧：尝试从 morning_scan 写入的实时指数 JSON 读取盘中涨跌\n        logging.warning(\n            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] {normalized_code} 数据陈旧（最后日期={latest_date_key}，\"\n            f\"今日={today_key}），尝试读取实时指数数据...\"\n        )\n        # 尝试从 realtime_index_returns.json 读取盘中涨跌\n        realtime_path = PROJECT_ROOT.parent / \"daily_stock_analysis\" / \"realtime_index_returns.json\"\n        if realtime_path.exists():\n            try:\n                import json as _json\n                rt_data = _json.loads(realtime_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n                if rt_data.get(\"date\") == str(today_key):\n                    rt_returns = rt_data.get(\"returns\", {})\n                    # normalized_code 可能是 ZZ2000 / HS300 / ZZ500\n                    rt_val = rt_returns.get(normalized_code)\n                    if rt_val is not None:\n                        logging.warning(\n                            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] 使用 realtime JSON 盘中涨跌 \"\n                            f\"{normalized_code}={rt_val:.2f}%\"\n                        )\n                        return float(rt_val)\n            except Exception:\n                pass\n        logging.warning(\n            f\"[load_index_return_pct_for_date] 盘中实时数据不可用，返回 0.0。\"\n            f\"请确认 morning_scan 已成功运行并更新了实时指数数据。\"\n        )\n        return 0.0"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75715,"output":551,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773972409024}}
