{"type":"message","id":"22f9bb64","parentId":"56c98a79","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:30:10.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's 1 WARN issue: `event_watch_mode_mismatch` - event_watch shows `halt` but runtime shows `normal`. This is the `-2.31%` issue we already fixed. Let me also do a broader ad-hoc self-check that covers all the issues we found today:1. 指数数据陈旧（昨天-2.31%冒充今日）→ 已修复\n2. 预算120万问题 → 已修复\n3. 扫码登录页快速关闭 → 修复已实施，待实测\n4. event_watch_mode_mismatch → 相关到指数数据陈旧修复\n\nLet me also check for any other potential issues. But actually, the user said \"太多问题了，你想办法再做个全面自检\" - they want me to do a comprehensive check. Let me do a more thorough review of the day's findings and verify the fixes are all in place.","thinkingSignature":"e6ed359b526d6023448f4afe7b4f89b9da85069f3db70b7c7fc74b00b2cdf6c1"},{"type":"text","text":" tester 跑出来了，有 1 个 WARN：`event_watch halt/runtime normal 不匹配`——这是今天 `-2.31%` 陈旧数据问题的延续，我们已经修了。但让我再做一轮更广的全面自检，覆盖今天发现的所有问题：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lq66dpvs8yfl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nprint('=== 全面自检 ===')\nprint()\n\n# 1. 指数数据陈旧检查\nprint('【1】指数数据新鲜度检查')\nDATA_ROOT = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis')\nfrom datetime import date\ntoday = int(date.today().strftime('%Y%m%d'))\nfor fname in ['index_000852_SH.csv', 'index_000300_SH.csv']:\n    fpath = DATA_ROOT / fname\n    if fpath.exists():\n        import pandas as pd\n        df = pd.read_csv(fpath)\n        last_date = int(df.iloc[-1]['trade_date'])\n        status = '✅' if last_date == today else '❌ 陈旧'\n        print(f'  {fname}: 最后日期={last_date}, 今天={today} {status}')\n    else:\n        print(f'  {fname}: 文件不存在 ❌')\nprint()\n\n# 2. 预算配置检查\nprint('【2】三模拟盘日增预算检查（合计应=100万）')\nimport json\nconfigs = {\n    'defensive': '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/paper_live_trading_defensive_v1.json',\n    'balanced':  '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/paper_live_trading_balanced_v1.json',\n    'aggressive':'/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/paper_live_trading_aggressive_v1.json',\n}\ntotal = 0\nfor name, path in configs.items():\n    d = json.load(open(path))\n    r = d['execution']['max_daily_add_ratio']\n    b = r * 1000000\n    total += b\n    print(f'  {name:10s}: {r:.3f} → {b/10000:.2f}万/日')\nprint(f'  {'合计':10s}: {total/10000:.2f}万  {\\\"✅\\\" if abs(total-1000000)<100 else \\\"❌ 异常\\\"}')\nprint()\n\n# 3. runtime_risk_state 中的 index_ret_pct 检查\nprint('【3】runtime_risk_state 的 index_ret_pct 检查（今日应为0或实时值）')\nrpath = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/runtime_risk_state_latest.json')\nif rpath.exists():\n    d = json.load(open(rpath))\n    ret = d.get('runtime_metrics', {}).get('index_ret_pct', 'N/A')\n    print(f'  index_ret_pct={ret}  {\\\"✅ 合理（已修复）\\\" if abs(float(ret or 0)) < 0.01 else \\\"❌ 仍为昨日数据\\\"}')\nprint()\n\n# 4. 小红书扫码登录修复检查\nprint('【4】小红书扫码登录修复检查')\nlogin_f = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshu-skills/scripts/xhs/login.py')\ncli_f = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshu-skills/scripts/cli.py')\nupdate_sh = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/update_xhs_web_session.sh')\nfor f, name in [(login_f, 'login.py'), (cli_f, 'cli.py'), (update_sh, 'update_xhs_web_session.sh')]:\n    content = f.read_text() if f.exists() else ''\n    has_new_sig = 'initial_qr_data_url' in content or 'qr_refreshed' in content or 'new_qr_url' in content\n    print(f'  {name}: {\\\"✅ 已修复\\\" if has_new_sig else \\\"⚠️ 需检查\\\"}')\nprint()\n\n# 5. event_watch halt 状态来源检查\nprint('【5】event_watch halt 来源（今日 index_ret_pct）')\new_path = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_event_watch_20260320.json')\nif ew_path.exists():\n    d = json.load(open(ew_path))\n    halt_reason = str(d.get('triggers', [{}])[0].get('halt_reason', '') if d.get('triggers') else d.get('current', {}).get('halt_reason', ''))\n    print(f'  halt_reason: {halt_reason}')\n    if '-2.31' in halt_reason:\n        print('  ❌ 仍使用昨日数据')\n    elif 'index_ret_pct(0.0)' in halt_reason or '0.00' in halt_reason:\n        print('  ✅ 已使用修复后的数据（0.0）')\n    else:\n        print('  ⚠️ 需要进一步检查')\nprint()\n\nprint('=== 自检完成 ===')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85112,"output":1342,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773980985873}}
