{"type":"message","id":"99c6d557","parentId":"9ed026ec","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:32:11.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. In the `else` branch (lines 115-118), when `gate_action` is not \"halt\" and not \"cautious\" (i.e., \"none\"), and breadth is unavailable, it just keeps the base runtime without changing mode. This is the bug.\n\nThe fix should be: when `gate_action == \"none\"` but `breadth_available == False`, the system should go to `cautious` or at least not stay `normal`.\n\nLet me look at the full context of this else branch.","thinkingSignature":"ab46c5a0d1ec3d3707fd1ed555358a6201c60f7cdae6fe89db22bf37ffd8da80"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x5jb9rmmub1w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '75,125p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93506,"output":186,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981125559}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb90a671","parentId":"99c6d557","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:32:11.648Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x5jb9rmmub1w_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                    \"market_breadth\": breadth_ratio if breadth_available else None,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_market_halt\"]))\n        else:\n            # 非 halt 时，盘中宽度缺失不再一刀切 halt，而是回退到更保守但可持续的状态。\n            if not breadth_available:\n                base_mode = str(intraday_runtime.get(\"mode\") or \"normal\")\n                if base_mode == \"halt\" or bool(intraday_runtime.get(\"hard_stop\")):\n                    intraday_runtime[\"intraday_gate_applied\"] = True\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_keep_base\"])\n                    )\n                elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": \"盘中宽度不可用，按指数门禁进入 cautious\",\n                 