{"type":"message","id":"95670a9a","parentId":"45c2ccc4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:34:05.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue clearly:1. `event_watch halt_reason` = \"盘中宽度不可用，禁止自动恢复买入\" → This is from the paper execution system's intraday breadth check, not from the pre-market breadth of 0.092.2. `runtime_metrics.market_breadth` = 0.377 → This is the pre-market breadth (computed before the market opened), which is healthy.\n3. `latest_runtime.mode` = normal → The intraday gate is disabled (non-trading hours), so the breadth check is bypassed.The issue is that `event_watch` is correctly applying the breadth halt when breadth is unavailable (during non-trading hours), but `runtime_risk_state` is not.\n\n\nThe problem is that when the intraday gate is disabled during non-trading hours, `runtime_risk_state` keeps the `base_runtime` mode of normal, even though it should recognize that breadth data is unavailable and treat that as a risk condition. I need to modify `run_intraday_risk_recheck.py` to ensure that when the gate is disabled but breadth is unavailable, the system still flags this appropriately rather than proceeding as if everything is normal.","thinkingSignature":"4172f2ce56034a6148dad641aca6f42fd5b6d28de3ff67b7b8df95b8382830c9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fym300awtqwj_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py","oldText":"    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")","newText":"    # 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎\n    if not intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        runtime_breadth = runtime_metrics.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        if runtime_breadth is not None and runtime_breadth < breadth_riskoff:\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"cautious\" if runtime_breadth >= breadth_hard_stop else \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"预市场宽度 {runtime_breadth:.3f} < {breadth_riskoff:.3f}，盘中门禁未启用\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": False,\n                    \"market_breadth\": runtime_breadth,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = [\"premarket_breadth_riskoff\"]\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93426,"output":590,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118893,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981233616}}
