{"type":"message","id":"c301a50c","parentId":"bb7fa598","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:34:34.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see! The paper execution system's `market_breadth = 0.092` is much lower than `runtime_metrics.market_breadth = 0.377`. These are two different breadth computations!\n\nThe paper execution uses the `market_breadth` field from the strategy audit or precheck, which is the pre-market market breadth (all stocks above their moving averages). This is 0.092 - extremely low, which triggers the halt.\n\nBut `runtime_metrics.market_breadth = 0.377` comes from somewhere else - likely the `intraday_breadth` from the market probe, which is different.\n\nSo the issue is:1. \n\nThe paper execution system is using 0.092 from the pre-market scan (checking how many stocks are above their moving averages), while the runtime risk state is using 0.377 from a different intraday breadth calculation. The tester is catching this mismatch where event_watch shows halt mode due to the low 0.092 breadth, but runtime_risk_state shows normal because it's pulling a different market breadth metric. The fix would be to align what runtime_risk_state uses for its breadth calculation.","thinkingSignature":"20139f3c1721ceb76c0684d88030ba47fd250d49493ce4c2e4e87297edbe0cf7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6u7hme8n2a4n_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py","oldText":"    # 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎\n    if not intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        runtime_breadth = runtime_metrics.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        if runtime_breadth is not None and runtime_breadth < breadth_riskoff:\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"cautious\" if runtime_breadth >= breadth_hard_stop else \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"预市场宽度 {runtime_breadth:.3f} < {breadth_riskoff:.3f}，盘中门禁未启用\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": False,\n                    \"market_breadth\": runtime_breadth,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = [\"premarket_breadth_riskoff\"]\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")","newText":"    # 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎\n    # 注意：runtime_metrics.market_breadth 与 paper_execution.market_breadth 可能来自不同数据源\n    # 两者都低于阈值时应统一触发 halt，避免 event_watch 与 runtime_risk_state 状态不一致\n    if not intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        runtime_breadth = runtime_metrics.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        if runtime_breadth is not None and runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop:\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"市场宽度 {runtime_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}，盘中门禁未启用但宽度极低\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": False,\n                    \"market_breadth\": runtime_breadth,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = [\"premarket_breadth_hard_stop\"]\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93265,"output":829,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118971,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981259181}}
