{"type":"message","id":"2401686f","parentId":"1bfcba6a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:28.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see it clearly:\n\n1. At 09:47, 10:14, 11:00: `market_breadth = 0.092` → `mode = halt` (正确)\n2. At 12:07, 12:32: `market_breadth = 0.377` → `mode = normal` (错误！)\n\nThe market_breadth jumped from 0.092 to 0.377 at 12:07. This is because the market opened at 09:30 and by noon the breadth calculation changed.\n\nBut more importantly, at 12:07 the `mode = normal` because:\n\n\n- `market_breadth = 0.377` exceeds the `breadth_riskoff = 0.35` threshold, so it doesn't trigger the cautious threshold, and `market_breadth = 0.377` > `breadth_hard_stop = 0.25`, so it also doesn't trigger halt.\n\nThe halt reason from event_watch is \"盘中宽度不可用，禁止自动恢复买入\" — meaning the breadth computation for paper execution used a different data source at 09:45 than what the intraday risk recheck is using now, and this breadth has since recovered from 0.092 to 0.377.\n\nThe tester flag is correct: there's a genuine state inconsistency. The paper execution halted at 09:47 when breadth was 0.092, but the current runtime_risk_state shows normal mode with breadth at 0.377. Since 0.377 > 0.35, the runtime is actually correct to be in normal mode now — it's not stale data, the market breadth genuinely improved around 11:00-12:00. However, the halt should only clear if the breadth remains above the risk threshold for a sustained period.\n\nThe real problem seems to be a timing issue in how `runtime_risk_state_latest` gets updated. The morning precheck ran at 08:40 with the old 03-19 data that had market_breadth at 0.092, then the intraday recheck ran at 09:47 and correctly set mode to halt. But sometime between 11:00 and 12:07, the breadth calculation changed or the file got overwritten, and now it shows 0.377 with normal mode. This could be a data pipeline issue where Qlib's breadth calculation refreshed with new market data, or the stale pre-market snapshot got replaced with fresh intraday data.","thinkingSignature":"a0f052871af6ebfa3c3cb41bc8194cb4f7257d9da68ec02740fefc609c7c4692"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ijl0fxdw6bn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfiles = [\n    '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/intraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1100.json',\n    '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/intraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1207.json',\n]\nfor f in files:\n    d = json.load(open(f))\n    print(f.split('/')[-1])\n    print('  generated_at:', d.get('generated_at'))\n    print('  runtime_metrics.market_breadth:', d.get('runtime_metrics', {}).get('market_breadth'))\n    print('  latest_runtime.mode:', d.get('latest_runtime', {}).get('mode'))\n    print('  intraday_breadth:', {k: d.get('intraday_breadth', {}).get(k) for k in ['available', 'up_ratio'] if d.get('intraday_breadth', {}).get(k) is not None})\n\" 2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90806,"output":787,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116470,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981365866}}
{"type":"message","id":"95a011f9","parentId":"2401686f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:28.336Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2ijl0fxdw6bn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"intraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1100.json\n  generated_at: 2026-03-20 11:00:45\n  runtime_metrics.market_breadth: 0.09200438116100766\n  latest_runtime.mode: halt\n  intraday_breadth: {'available': False}\nintraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1207.json\n  generated_at: 2026-03-20 12:07:17\n  runtime_metrics.market_breadth: 0.37697066453801636\n  latest_runtime.mode: normal\n  intraday_breadth: {'available': False}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":39,"aggregated":"intraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1100.json\n  generated_at: 2026-03-20 11:00:45\n  runtime_metrics.market_breadth: 0.09200438116100766\n  latest_runtime.mode: halt\n  intraday_breadth: {'available': False}\nintraday_risk_recheck_20260320_1207.json\n  generated_at: 2026-03-20 12:07:17\n  runtime_metrics.market_breadth: 0.37697066453801636\n  latest_runtime.mode: normal\n  intraday_breadth: {'available': False}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773981388326}}
{"type":"message","id":"15c8b62f","parentId":"95a011f9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:45.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see it now. The `intraday_breadth.available = False` in both cases. But `runtime_metrics.market_breadth` changed from 0.092 to 0.377 between 11:00 and 12:07. This is a data refresh - the pre-market breadth calculation refreshed with new data between these two runs.\n\nSince `runtime_metrics.market_breadth = 0.377 > 0.35` (riskoff threshold), the mode is `normal`. This is actually correct behavior!\n\nThe `event_watch` halt is based on the fact that `intraday_breadth.available = False`. When intraday breadth is not available, the system should not auto-restore from halt. The halt reason says \"盘中宽度不可用，禁止自动恢复买入\". This is a policy decision: don't restore from halt if we can't verify the market breadth is healthy.\n\n\nThe tester is flagging an inconsistency between `event_watch` showing `mode=halt` and `runtime_risk_state` showing `mode=normal`, but this isn't really a bug—it's reflecting the difference between what halt_reason says (\"don't auto-restore\") versus what mode indicates. The core issue is whether these two systems should be aligned or if they serve different purposes. To fix this properly, I need to make sure `runtime_risk_state` also respects the \"no auto-restore without breadth\" constraint when `intraday_breadth.available=False`. The `latest_runtime.mode=normal` with `intraday_breadth.available=False` is problematic because it signals the system is in a normal state when we actually don't have visibility into intraday conditions to make that determination.","thinkingSignature":"cd639b674040efbc5290c80bac5d5e6a0f40e88b64ebd64a232f263aaed62b32"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tdrrmuhspwnd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '66,75p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91143,"output":419,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116439,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981388338}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6e40ac1","parentId":"15c8b62f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:45.848Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tdrrmuhspwnd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"intraday_runtime = dict(base_runtime)\n    intraday_runtime[\"intraday_gate_applied\"] = False\n\n    risk_cfg = config.get(\"risk\") or {}\n    breadth_hard_stop = float(risk_cfg.get(\"market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold\", 0.25) or 0.25)\n    breadth_riskoff = float(risk_cfg.get(\"market_breadth_riskoff_threshold\", 0.35) or 0.35)\n    breadth_available = bool(intraday_breadth.get(\"available\"))\n    breadth_ratio = intraday_breadth.get(\"up_ratio\")\n\n    # 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"intraday_runtime = dict(base_runtime)\n    intraday_runtime[\"intraday_gate_applied\"] = False\n\n    risk_cfg = config.get(\"risk\") or {}\n    breadth_hard_stop = float(risk_cfg.get(\"market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold\", 0.25) or 0.25)\n    breadth_riskoff = float(risk_cfg.get(\"market_breadth_riskoff_threshold\", 0.35) or 0.35)\n    breadth_available = bool(intraday_breadth.get(\"available\"))\n    breadth_ratio = intraday_breadth.get(\"up_ratio\")\n\n    # 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773981405838}}
{"type":"message","id":"3509faa0","parentId":"f6e40ac1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:54.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to fix the block where `intraday_gate.enabled == False` (non-trading hours). The fix should be: when `intraday_breadth.available == False` AND `gate_action == \"none\"` (gate disabled), we should NOT fall back to `normal` mode - we should keep or set `halt` or `cautious`.\n\nLet me now look at the complete flow when `intraday_gate.enabled == False`.","thinkingSignature":"2dfcdf3111aa9744ada135771e762659af0154bbc425a4b04221610660d52dd7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_57n3gfeiydtp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '75,175p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90311,"output":168,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773981405850}}
{"type":"message","id":"d89dc120","parentId":"3509faa0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:36:54.906Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_57n3gfeiydtp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎\n    # 注意：runtime_metrics.market_breadth 与 paper_execution.market_breadth 可能来自不同数据源\n    # 两者都低于阈值时应统一触发 halt，避免 event_watch 与 runtime_risk_state 状态不一致\n    if not intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        runtime_breadth = runtime_metrics.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        if runtime_breadth is not None and runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop:\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"市场宽度 {runtime_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}，盘中门禁未启用但宽度极低\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": False,\n                    \"market_breadth\": runtime_breadth,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = [\"premarket_breadth_hard_stop\"]\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                    \"market_breadth\": breadth_ratio if breadth_available else None,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_market_halt\"]))\n        else:\n            # 非 halt 时，盘中宽度缺失不再一刀切 halt，而是回退到更保守但可持续的状态。\n            if not breadth_available:\n                base_mode = str(intraday_runtime.get(\"mode\") or \"normal\")\n                if base_mode == \"halt\" or bool(intraday_runtime.get(\"hard_stop\")):\n                    intraday_runtime[\"intraday_gate_applied\"] = True\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_keep_base\"])\n                    )\n                elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": \"盘中宽度不可用，按指数门禁进入 cautious\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_cautious\"])\n                    )\n                else:\n                    # gate_action == \"none\" 但盘中宽度不可用时，\n                    # 为防止误在正常模式自动买入，应降至 cautious\n                    base_mode = str(intraday_runtime.get(\"mode\") or \"normal\")\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\" if base_mode == \"normal\" else base_mode,\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": \"盘中宽度不可用，禁止激进自动操作\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_cautious\"])\n                    )\n            else:\n                intraday_runtime[\"market_breadth\"] = breadth_ratio\n                if breadth_ratio is not None and breadth_ratio <= breadth_hard_stop:\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": True,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                            \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中宽度 {breadth_ratio:.3f} <= hard_stop {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_halt\"]))\n                elif gate_action == \"cautious\" or (breadth_ratio is not None and breadth_ratio <= breadth_riskoff):\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中恢复至 cautious：指数/宽度仍偏弱（breadth={breadth_ratio:.3f}）\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_market_cautious\"]))"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"# 即使盘中门禁未启用（午间休市等），若预市场宽度极低也应触发谨慎\n    # 注意：runtime_metrics.market_breadth 与 paper_execution.market_breadth 可能来自不同数据源\n    # 两者都低于阈值时应统一触发 halt，避免 event_watch 与 runtime_risk_state 状态不一致\n    if not intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        runtime_breadth = runtime_metrics.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        if runtime_breadth is not None and runtime_breadth < breadth_hard_stop:\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"市场宽度 {runtime_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}，盘中门禁未启用但宽度极低\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": False,\n                    \"market_breadth\": runtime_breadth,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = [\"premarket_breadth_hard_stop\"]\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            intraday_runtime.update(\n                {\n                    \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                    \"risk_off\": True,\n                    \"hard_stop\": True,\n                    \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                    \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\",\n                    \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                    \"market_breadth\": breadth_ratio if breadth_available else None,\n                }\n            )\n            intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_market_halt\"]))\n        else:\n            # 非 halt 时，盘中宽度缺失不再一刀切 halt，而是回退到更保守但可持续的状态。\n            if not breadth_available:\n                base_mode = str(intraday_runtime.get(\"mode\") or \"normal\")\n                if base_mode == \"halt\" or bool(intraday_runtime.get(\"hard_stop\")):\n                    intraday_runtime[\"intraday_gate_applied\"] = True\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_keep_base\"])\n                    )\n                elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": \"盘中宽度不可用，按指数门禁进入 cautious\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_cautious\"])\n                    )\n                else:\n                    # gate_action == \"none\" 但盘中宽度不可用时，\n                    # 为防止误在正常模式自动买入，应降至 cautious\n                    base_mode = str(intraday_runtime.get(\"mode\") or \"normal\")\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\" if base_mode == \"normal\" else base_mode,\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": \"盘中宽度不可用，禁止激进自动操作\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(\n                        dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_unavailable_cautious\"])\n                    )\n            else:\n                intraday_runtime[\"market_breadth\"] = breadth_ratio\n                if breadth_ratio is not None and breadth_ratio <= breadth_hard_stop:\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"halt\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": True,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": True,\n                            \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中宽度 {breadth_ratio:.3f} <= hard_stop {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_breadth_halt\"]))\n                elif gate_action == \"cautious\" or (breadth_ratio is not None and breadth_ratio <= breadth_riskoff):\n                    intraday_runtime.update(\n                        {\n                            \"mode\": \"cautious\",\n                            \"risk_off\": True,\n                            \"hard_stop\": False,\n                            \"halt_new_buy\": False,\n                            \"halt_reason\": f\"盘中恢复至 cautious：指数/宽度仍偏弱（breadth={breadth_ratio:.3f}）\",\n                            \"intraday_gate_applied\": True,\n                        }\n                    )\n                    intraday_runtime[\"gate_reasons\"] = list(dict.fromkeys((intraday_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or []) + [\"intraday_market_cautious\"]))","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773981414889}}
