{"type":"message","id":"f7acba60","parentId":"64c96c81","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:34:30.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the complete picture. Let me summarize all the bugs found:\n\n**Bug 1 (HIGH - already identified by Tester)**: `apply_runtime_overlay` in `run_investment_research_event_watch.py` has two overlay blocks. The second block overwrites the `mode` set by the first (runtime_risk_state) block with `report_obj.risk_mode = \"normal\"` from the morning strategy report. This causes the cautious mode from intraday recheck to be overwritten.\n\n**Fix**: Change the second overlay block to use `setdefault` or `pe.setdefault(\"mode\", ...)` instead of direct assignment.\n \nThe Tester ALERT flags a third issue where the runtime and report breadth values diverge at 0.2716 versus 0.3769—two separate systems pulling different market breadth sources. I need to verify whether this stems from stale data or an intentional architectural split between intraday breadth monitoring and morning breadth analysis. Let me trace the fix and move forward.","thinkingSignature":"d7012a0954c31fb30925068308406d13ac7ed0490d9979a1cee4d8f1aa0024fe"},{"type":"text","text":"根因定位到了。`apply_runtime_overlay` 里第二个 block 在覆盖第一个 block 设置的 `cautious` mode——直接修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fezcs2q67zue_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py","oldText":"    trade_date_text = str(report_obj.get(\"trade_date\") or \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\")\n    if trade_date_text == date_tag and report_obj:\n        pe = dict(summary.get(\"paper_execution_status\") or {})\n        pe.setdefault(\"source\", \"strategy_report\")\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\") is not None:\n            pe[\"mode\"] = report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\")\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_off\") is not None:\n            pe[\"risk_off\"] = report_obj.get(\"risk_off\")\n            summary[\"risk_off\"] = bool(report_obj.get(\"risk_off\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\") is not None:\n            pe[\"hard_stop\"] = report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\")\n        if report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\") is not None:\n            pe[\"halt_new_buy\"] = report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\")\n            pe[\"allowed_to_open_new_positions\"] = not bool(report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\"):\n            pe[\"halt_reason\"] = report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\")\n        if \"market_breadth\" in report_obj:\n            pe[\"market_breadth\"] = report_obj.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        summary[\"paper_execution_status\"] = pe","newText":"    # 注意：第二个 overlay 块不得覆盖第一个 runtime_risk_state 块已设置的字段，\n    # 因为 runtime_risk_state 含有盘中实时门控，比 morning strategy report 更新鲜。\n    # 只在 runtime_risk_state 无数据时才用 strategy_report 的值做 fallback。\n    trade_date_text = str(report_obj.get(\"trade_date\") or \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\")\n    if trade_date_text == date_tag and report_obj and not latest_runtime:\n        pe = dict(summary.get(\"paper_execution_status\") or {})\n        pe.setdefault(\"source\", \"strategy_report\")\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"mode\", report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_off\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"risk_off\", report_obj.get(\"risk_off\"))\n            summary.setdefault(\"risk_off\", bool(report_obj.get(\"risk_off\")))\n        if report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"hard_stop\", report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"halt_new_buy\", report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\"))\n            pe.setdefault(\"allowed_to_open_new_positions\", not bool(report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\")))\n        if report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\"):\n            pe.setdefault(\"halt_reason\", report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\"))\n        if \"market_breadth\" in report_obj:\n            pe.setdefault(\"market_breadth\", report_obj.get(\"market_breadth\"))\n        summary[\"paper_execution_status\"] = pe"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99092,"output":910,"cacheRead":24756,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124758,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773988441792}}
