{"type":"message","id":"702e951a","parentId":"d82468f1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:51:56.040Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hunmtc598q6h_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def evaluate_runtime_state_for_date(\n    *,\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    live_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    date_tag: str,\n    index_ret_pct: float,\n    market_breadth: float | None,\n) -> RuntimeState:\n    combo = live_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {}) or {}\n    max_dd = parse_float(combo.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\"), 0.0)\n    sharpe = parse_float(combo.get(\"sharpe\"), 0.0)\n    target_dd = parse_float((config.get(\"targets\") or {}).get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot_for_date(config, date_tag)\n\n    runtime_risk_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=target_dd)\n    engine = RiskEngine(runtime_risk_cfg)\n    decision = engine.evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=tag_to_iso(date_tag),\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=index_ret_pct,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=max_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\")),\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\")),\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\")),\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\")),\n        )\n    )\n    halt_reason = decision.reason or (decision.reasons[0] if decision.reasons else \"\")\n    return RuntimeState(\n        date_tag=parse_date_tag(date_tag),\n        mode=decision.mode,\n        halt_new_buy=decision.halt_new_buy,\n        halt_reason=halt_reason,\n        risk_off=decision.risk_off,\n        hard_stop=decision.hard_stop,\n        market_breadth=market_breadth,\n        gate_reasons=decision.reasons,\n        style_snapshot=style_snapshot,\n    )"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"def evaluate_runtime_state_for_date(\n    *,\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    live_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    date_tag: str,\n    index_ret_pct: float,\n    market_breadth: float | None,\n) -> RuntimeState:\n    combo = live_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {}) or {}\n    max_dd = parse_float(combo.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\"), 0.0)\n    sharpe = parse_float(combo.get(\"sharpe\"), 0.0)\n    target_dd = parse_float((config.get(\"targets\") or {}).get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot_for_date(config, date_tag)\n\n    runtime_risk_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=target_dd)\n    engine = RiskEngine(runtime_risk_cfg)\n    decision = engine.evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=tag_to_iso(date_tag),\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=index_ret_pct,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=max_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\")),\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\")),\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\")),\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\")),\n        )\n    )\n    halt_reason = decision.reason or (decision.reasons[0] if decision.reasons else \"\")\n    return RuntimeState(\n        date_tag=parse_date_tag(date_tag),\n        mode=decision.mode,\n        halt_new_buy=decision.halt_new_buy,\n        halt_reason=halt_reason,\n        risk_off=decision.risk_off,\n        hard_stop=decision.hard_stop,\n        market_breadth=market_breadth,\n        gate_reasons=decision.reasons,\n        style_snapshot=style_snapshot,\n    )","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993116023}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c470eaf","parentId":"702e951a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:16.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the `evaluate_runtime_state_for_date` creates a `RuntimeState` with `halt_new_buy=decision.halt_new_buy`. The `decision` comes from `RiskEngine.evaluate_runtime_state()`.Let me now look at the actual execution brief for 20260319 to see what `halt_new_buy` value it reported at generation time.\n\nThe execution brief says:- `market_breadth: 0.649` (from `runtime_metrics` which was the PRE-INTRADAY value, not the intraday value)\n- `zz2000_ret_pct: 0.96%` (from `runtime_metrics` which was also stale data)The key question is: what was `runtime.halt_new_buy` when `size_orders` was called for 20260319?\n\n\nAt the point when `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` ran for 20260319, it fetched `runtime_metrics` from `load_runtime_metrics_for_date()`, which had a stale `index_ret_pct` of +0.96% from the CSV (still on 03/18 data as of 03/19 morning). The RiskEngine then evaluated this stale data and set `halt_new_buy` to False since the index return wasn't negative enough to trigger a halt. So `evaluate_runtime_state_for_date` was working with outdated information.\n\nNow I'm realizing the critical issue: the intraday recheck that detected the halt (4/4 indices down) ran separately from `prepare_paper_orders_v1`, and it wasn't being read or applied by the paper execution pipeline at all. The paper orders were generated using stale morning metrics instead of the real-time intraday signals, which is why the halt condition wasn't being respected.","thinkingSignature":"978625b4d72e6029e49fefdd995b0ded97089629bb011e0f7006b699c985b5d7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2dztbndadzla_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"intraday_gate\\|get_intraday_market\\|market_state\\|halt_new_buy\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py | head -20","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97473,"output":446,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993116043}}
