{"type":"message","id":"98e4d321","parentId":"f6029dc7","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:33.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so at line 536-537, the script gets `intraday_gate` and checks if it's enabled. If it is, it overrides `runtime.halt_new_buy`. The issue must be that for 20260319, the `get_intraday_market_state()` was NOT enabled (returned `enabled=False`), so the halt check was skipped entirely!\n\nLet me verify this by checking the execution brief for 20260319 - does it show \"盘中实时门禁\" details?","thinkingSignature":"1dc54a1b83527152d8a84ef3c8df5ce1ff6bff2449318df836a9641c6ff6c92d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eyg2veexjg3b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"intraday_gate\\|盘中实时\\|门禁触发\\|gate_action\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_defensive_execution_brief_v1_20260319.md 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97104,"output":202,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122183,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993136740}}
