{"type":"message","id":"c9f02320","parentId":"3bc89f19","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:40.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 20260319 brief doesn't mention intraday gate! This confirms that `intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\")` was False for 20260319 when `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` ran. So the intraday halt was never applied to paper orders.\n\nBut wait - the `get_intraday_market_state()` should return `enabled=True` for trading hours on a trading day. Let me check the intraday gate logic.","thinkingSignature":"cf789b84bebc146435f3794a1925859705a71addd5f46cd4dfdb74dc44cca939"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7f7r5qvwwy68_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"def get_intraday_market_state\\|enabled.*return\\|return.*enabled\\|enabled\\s*=\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/intraday_market_gate.py | head -20","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97324,"output":183,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122384,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993153884}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d41f234","parentId":"c9f02320","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:40.766Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7f7r5qvwwy68_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"210:def get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n221:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n224:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"210:def get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n221:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n224:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993160750}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a6f9b48","parentId":"0d41f234","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:58.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The function returns `enabled=False` if it's not a trading hour. The `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` runs at a specific time. For the 20260319 morning run, it likely ran at ~08:40-09:20, which is BEFORE market open (09:30). So `get_intraday_market_state()` would return `enabled=False` (non-trading hours) because it's 08:40 and the market hasn't opened yet!That's the real bug. The morning run (which generates paper orders) happens BEFORE market open, so the intraday gate always returns `enabled=False` for the morning run. The orders are generated with the OLD runtime state (from CSV data, which is still T-1), and the halt check never happens.Then during the day, when the intraday recheck runs and detects halt, it updates the `runtime_risk_state_latest.json`. But the paper orders are ALREADY generated and committed by then.\nSo the fix needs to happen at the source: when generating orders in the morning, I should be pulling the latest runtime state from `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` (which gets updated by the intraday recheck) and checking `halt_new_buy` there, rather than relying on the intraday gate to be enabled during pre-market hours.","thinkingSignature":"60890aa2e59f3c96d98e7a2388e230a0e9b6e92f8a6234e800f6d0f8f0c7faec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_17ulbgnq0nlj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"get_intraday_market_state\\|enabled.*False\\|非交易时段\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/intraday_market_gate.py | head -20","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97258,"output":358,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993160770}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5ff3764","parentId":"0a6f9b48","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:52:58.281Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_17ulbgnq0nlj_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"163:            \"enabled\": False,\n175:            \"enabled\": False,\n210:def get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n215:    否则返回 {\"enabled\": False}\n221:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n224:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}\n235:    result = get_intraday_market_state(date_arg)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"163:            \"enabled\": False,\n175:            \"enabled\": False,\n210:def get_intraday_market_state(date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n215:    否则返回 {\"enabled\": False}\n221:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": f\"非今日({date_tag})\"}\n224:        return {\"enabled\": False, \"reason\": \"非交易时段\"}\n235:    result = get_intraday_market_state(date_arg)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993178266}}
{"type":"message","id":"a28aedef","parentId":"a5ff3764","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:22.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `get_intraday_market_state` function returns `enabled=False` before market open (before 09:30). This means the morning paper order generation doesn't apply the intraday gate halt check!\n\nThe fix should be: in `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py`, before generating orders, ALSO check the latest `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` for `halt_new_buy` status. The latest runtime (from the LAST intraday recheck run) may have a more recent assessment.\n\nBut actually, the morning orders run BEFORE the intraday recheck has run (because the intraday recheck runs starting from 10:00). \n\nSo the issue is timing: the morning script runs around 08:40-09:20, the intraday recheck doesn't run until 10:00, and the CSV data from 03/18 shows `index_ret_pct=+0.96%` which doesn't look alarming, but when the intraday recheck finally runs at 10:00 and sees the actual market conditions, it detects a halt condition.\n\nThe real problem is that the pre-market orders are generated using stale data with a normal runtime, so they slip through before the intraday check can catch them. I need to ensure that if the previous day's intraday recheck already flagged `halt_new_buy=True`, that status carries forward into the morning orders. The solution is to load and check the latest `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` before generating morning orders to see if there's a pending halt from the prior session.\n\nNow I'm tracing where `halt_new_buy` actually comes from in the runtime state—it originates from `evaluate_runtime_state_for_date` through the RiskEngine, not directly from the intraday gate itself.","thinkingSignature":"f31b52870fa20bead9f6c68c40af1e8724089e6c17450e8504ec19967df10149"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uhsop3qoqarn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# Check the latest runtime before 20260319 morning\nREPORT = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\nfiles = sorted(REPORT.glob('intraday_risk_recheck_20260318*.json'))\nprint('20260318 intraday files:', [f.name for f in files])\nif files:\n    d = json.load(open(files[-1]))\n    lr = d.get('latest_runtime', {})\n    print(f'  latest: {files[-1].name}')\n    print(f'  mode={lr.get(\\\"mode\\\")} halt={lr.get(\\\"halt_new_buy\\\")} halt_reason={str(lr.get(\\\"halt_reason\\\",\\\"\\\"))[:60]}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97332,"output":573,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993178284}}
{"type":"message","id":"d10c87af","parentId":"a28aedef","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:22.254Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uhsop3qoqarn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"20260318 intraday files: []"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":39,"aggregated":"20260318 intraday files: []","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993202244}}
{"type":"message","id":"357a73e0","parentId":"d10c87af","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:40.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No intraday recheck for 20260318! So there's no `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` before 20260319 morning. And even if there was, the morning pipeline doesn't read it.\n\nOK, the real fix is clear:\n\nIn `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py`, BEFORE calling `size_orders()`, if `intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\")` is False (which it always is in the morning), we should check the LATEST `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` (from yesterday's last intraday recheck if it exists) for `halt_new_buy` and apply it.\n \nBut there's a timing issue here - the morning pipeline runs before any intraday checks exist for the current day, and even if we check yesterday's final state, it won't have the updated index returns since the CSV data is still stale at that point. The halt_new_buy flag only gets set correctly when both the updated index data and intraday analysis are available.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the root cause is simpler - the paper orders are generated at 08:40 using yesterday's CSV data which still shows index returns of +0.96%, so no halt gets triggered then. By the time the intraday gate finally detects the halt condition at 10:00+, the orders are already placed. The fix is straightforward: check if yesterday's last intraday recheck already set halt_new_buy, and if so, apply that same halt state to today's morning pipeline.","thinkingSignature":"e10eb27d9b32767b67a491a0829c4ff3167a262606872762228b21dd9b8d19c5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qenel2k1fsj5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '533,558p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97609,"output":376,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122862,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993202257}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cbd396c","parentId":"357a73e0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:53:40.160Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qenel2k1fsj5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ===== 盘中实时大盘门禁 =====\n    # 在生成买入推荐前，先检查当日实时大盘状态\n    # 如果是今日且在交易时段，用实时指数门禁覆盖旧的口径\n    intraday_gate = get_intraday_market_state(date_tag)\n    intraday_gate_applied = False\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            # 盘中 4/4 指数下跌，直接 halt\n            runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n            runtime.risk_off = True\n            runtime.hard_stop = True\n            runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n            runtime.halt_reason = f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\"\n            runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n            runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_halt\")\n            intraday_gate_applied = True\n        elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n            # 盘中 2/4 指数下跌，降级到 cautious\n            if runtime.mode not in [\"halt\"]:\n                runtime.mode = \"cautious\"\n                if not runtime.risk_off:\n                    runtime.risk_off = True\n                runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n                runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_cautious\")\n                intraday_gate_applied = True"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"# ===== 盘中实时大盘门禁 =====\n    # 在生成买入推荐前，先检查当日实时大盘状态\n    # 如果是今日且在交易时段，用实时指数门禁覆盖旧的口径\n    intraday_gate = get_intraday_market_state(date_tag)\n    intraday_gate_applied = False\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            # 盘中 4/4 指数下跌，直接 halt\n            runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n            runtime.risk_off = True\n            runtime.hard_stop = True\n            runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n            runtime.halt_reason = f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\"\n            runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n            runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_halt\")\n            intraday_gate_applied = True\n        elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n            # 盘中 2/4 指数下跌，降级到 cautious\n            if runtime.mode not in [\"halt\"]:\n                runtime.mode = \"cautious\"\n                if not runtime.risk_off:\n                    runtime.risk_off = True\n                runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n                runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_cautious\")\n                intraday_gate_applied = True","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993220143}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca806bab","parentId":"6cbd396c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:54:15.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fix should be:\n1. If `intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\")` is False (morning before market open), also check the latest `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` from the PREVIOUS trading day\n2. If the previous day's runtime had `halt_new_buy=True`, carry it forward to today's morning orders\n\nLet me add this logic.","thinkingSignature":"485096dddc476429086ef2c0922452e66d3082a41c9cbf42439043e8882e7ca9"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了完整的根因链，现在修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hol0q9ddpyyy_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py","oldText":"    # ===== 盘中实时大盘门禁 =====\n    # 在生成买入推荐前，先检查当日实时大盘状态\n    # 如果是今日且在交易时段，用实时指数门禁覆盖旧的口径\n    intraday_gate = get_intraday_market_state(date_tag)\n    intraday_gate_applied = False\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            # 盘中 4/4 指数下跌，直接 halt\n            runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n            runtime.risk_off = True\n            runtime.hard_stop = True\n            runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n            runtime.halt_reason = f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\"\n            runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n            runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_halt\")\n            intraday_gate_applied = True\n        elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n            # 盘中 2/4 指数下跌，降级到 cautious\n            if runtime.mode not in [\"halt\"]:\n                runtime.mode = \"cautious\"\n                if not runtime.risk_off:\n                    runtime.risk_off = True\n                runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n                runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_cautious\")\n                intraday_gate_applied = True","newText":"    # ===== 盘中实时大盘门禁 =====\n    # 在生成买入推荐前，先检查当日实时大盘状态\n    # 如果是今日且在交易时段，用实时指数门禁覆盖旧的口径\n    intraday_gate = get_intraday_market_state(date_tag)\n    intraday_gate_applied = False\n\n    if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n        gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n        if gate_action == \"halt\":\n            # 盘中 4/4 指数下跌，直接 halt\n            runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n            runtime.risk_off = True\n            runtime.hard_stop = True\n            runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n            runtime.halt_reason = f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\"\n            runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n            runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_halt\")\n            intraday_gate_applied = True\n        elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n            # 盘中 2/4 指数下跌，降级到 cautious\n            if runtime.mode not in [\"halt\"]:\n                runtime.mode = \"cautious\"\n                if not runtime.risk_off:\n                    runtime.risk_off = True\n                runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n                runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_cautious\")\n                intraday_gate_applied = True\n    else:\n        # === 盘前门禁（当日开盘前）：\n        # intraday_gate.enabled=False 发生在：(1) 非交易时段 (2) 午间休市\n        # 盘前场景：CSV 数据仍为 T-1 日数据（次日开盘前不会更新），\n        # 导致基于今日指数收益率的 halt 判断失效。\n        # 修复：若上一个交易日收盘后的 intraday recheck 已记录 halt_new_buy=True，\n        # 则在盘前生成订单时也要继承该标志，防止用旧数据通过风控。\n        prev_date_tag = (\n            str(int(date_tag) - 1)\n            if len(date_tag) == 8 and date_tag >= datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n            else None\n        )\n        if prev_date_tag:\n            prev_rt_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"intraday_risk_recheck_{prev_date_tag}_2359.json\"\n            if not prev_rt_path.exists():\n                candidates = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(f\"intraday_risk_recheck_{prev_date_tag}_*.json\"))\n                prev_rt_path = candidates[-1] if candidates else None\n            if prev_rt_path and prev_rt_path.exists():\n                try:\n                    prev_rt = json.loads(prev_rt_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n                    prev_lr = prev_rt.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}\n                    if bool(prev_lr.get(\"halt_new_buy\")):\n                        runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n                        runtime.risk_off = True\n                        runtime.hard_stop = True\n                        runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n                        runtime.halt_reason = (\n                            f\"前日盘后门禁 halt 延续（{prev_rt.get('generated_at','?')}）：\"\n                            f\"{prev_lr.get('halt_reason', '未知原因')}\"\n                        )\n                        runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n                        runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"prev_day_intraday_halt_continuation\")\n                        intraday_gate_applied = False  # 盘前继承，非盘中触发\n                except Exception:\n                    pass"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97325,"output":1222,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993220163}}
{"type":"message","id":"0bd33614","parentId":"ca806bab","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:54:15.509Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hol0q9ddpyyy_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 534     # 在生成买入推荐前，先检查当日实时大盘状态\n 535     # 如果是今日且在交易时段，用实时指数门禁覆盖旧的口径\n 536     intraday_gate = get_intraday_market_state(date_tag)\n 537     intraday_gate_applied = False\n+538 \n 538     if intraday_gate.get(\"enabled\"):\n 539         gate_action = intraday_gate.get(\"gate_action\", \"none\")\n 540         if gate_action == \"halt\":\n 541             # 盘中 4/4 指数下跌，直接 halt\n 542             runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n 543             runtime.risk_off = True\n 544             runtime.hard_stop = True\n 545             runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n 546             runtime.halt_reason = f\"盘中门禁触发 halt: {intraday_gate.get('reason', '')}\"\n 547             runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n 548             runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_halt\")\n 549             intraday_gate_applied = True\n 550         elif gate_action == \"cautious\":\n 551             # 盘中 2/4 指数下跌，降级到 cautious\n 552             if runtime.mode not in [\"halt\"]:\n 553                 runtime.mode = \"cautious\"\n 554                 if not runtime.risk_off:\n 555                     runtime.risk_off = True\n 556                 runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n 557                 runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"intraday_market_cautious\")\n 558                 intraday_gate_applied = True\n+560     else:\n+561         # === 盘前门禁（当日开盘前）：\n+562         # intraday_gate.enabled=False 发生在：(1) 非交易时段 (2) 午间休市\n+563         # 盘前场景：CSV 数据仍为 T-1 日数据（次日开盘前不会更新），\n+564         # 导致基于今日指数收益率的 halt 判断失效。\n+565         # 修复：若上一个交易日收盘后的 intraday recheck 已记录 halt_new_buy=True，\n+566         # 则在盘前生成订单时也要继承该标志，防止用旧数据通过风控。\n+567         prev_date_tag = (\n+568             str(int(date_tag) - 1)\n+569             if len(date_tag) == 8 and date_tag >= datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n+570             else None\n+571         )\n+572         if prev_date_tag:\n+573             prev_rt_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"intraday_risk_recheck_{prev_date_tag}_2359.json\"\n+574             if not prev_rt_path.exists():\n+575                 candidates = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(f\"intraday_risk_recheck_{prev_date_tag}_*.json\"))\n+576                 prev_rt_path = candidates[-1] if candidates else None\n+577             if prev_rt_path and prev_rt_path.exists():\n+578                 try:\n+579                     prev_rt = json.loads(prev_rt_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n+580                     prev_lr = prev_rt.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}\n+581                     if bool(prev_lr.get(\"halt_new_buy\")):\n+582                         runtime.mode = \"halt\"\n+583                         runtime.risk_off = True\n+584                         runtime.hard_stop = True\n+585                         runtime.halt_new_buy = True\n+586                         runtime.halt_reason = (\n+587                             f\"前日盘后门禁 halt 延续（{prev_rt.get('generated_at','?')}）：\"\n+588                             f\"{prev_lr.get('halt_reason', '未知原因')}\"\n+589                         )\n+590                         runtime.gate_reasons = runtime.gate_reasons or []\n+591                         runtime.gate_reasons.append(\"prev_day_intraday_halt_continuation\")\n+592                         intraday_gate_applied = False  # 盘前继承，非盘中触发\n+593                 except Exception:\n+594                     pass\n 559 \n 560     rows, stats = size_orders(\n 561         tickets_path=tickets_path,\n 562         config=execution_cfg,\n     ...","firstChangedLine":538},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993255498}}
