{"type":"message","id":"a2487775","parentId":"39ab4271","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:59:45.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The simulation doesn't check halt_new_buy at all! The halt check happens at the orders generation stage, not in the simulation execution. So the simulation blindly fills all orders that reach it.\n\nThe key issue is: halt_new_buy gets set in prepare_paper_orders_v1.py, but if it doesn't get set (because intraday_gate.enabled=False), then orders pass through.\n\nMy fix already handles the inheritance case. Let me now think about what other preventive mechanisms make sense:\n\n1. ✅ **Done**: `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` - halt inheritance from previous day's last intraday recheck\n2. **CSV freshness warning**: Add warning when CSV data is stale on a trading day\n\n\n3. **Tester guard**: Add morning gate consistency check - if yesterday ended in halt and today has buys → flag\n4. **Simulation guard**: In `run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py`, check if halt_new_buy=True and today has buys → flag or auto-rollback\n\nFor the CSV freshness warning, I need to add it to `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` after loading runtime_metrics. Then I'll add a tester guard check in `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` to catch this scenario. For the simulation guard, I need to find where to inject the halt_new_buy check.\n\nLet me start implementing these.","thinkingSignature":"178aa8c67a79809b839cef225a4e0d9ade3bc3829f0d03fc9d6d300e75c9aaa0"},{"type":"text","text":"先在 `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` 加**第二层**——CSV 陈旧时打印明确警告：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lw27jccp8tjj_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py","oldText":"    holdings_map = load_holdings_map(holdings_dated)\n    adv20_map = load_adv20_map(A_STOCK_CSV, min_trade_date=\"2020-01-01\")\n    runtime_metrics = load_runtime_metrics_for_date(date_tag, execution_cfg, report_dir=REPORT_DIR)\n    live_payload = runtime_metrics[\"live_payload\"]","newText":"    holdings_map = load_holdings_map(holdings_dated)\n    adv20_map = load_adv20_map(A_STOCK_CSV, min_trade_date=\"2020-01-01\")\n    runtime_metrics = load_runtime_metrics_for_date(date_tag, execution_cfg, report_dir=REPORT_DIR)\n\n    # ===== CSV 数据新鲜度校验（防控 T-1 数据被误用）====\n    csv_index_file = DATA_ROOT / \"index_000852_SH.csv\"\n    csv_data_stale_warning = \"\"\n    if csv_index_file.exists():\n        import pandas as pd\n        df_idx = pd.read_csv(csv_index_file)\n        last_csv_date = int(df_idx.iloc[-1][\"trade_date\"])\n        today_int = int(datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n        if last_csv_date < today_int:\n            csv_data_stale_warning = (\n                f\"[WARN] CSV 指数数据陈旧（最后日期={last_csv_date}，今日={today_int}），\"\n                f\"index_ret_pct 可能为昨日数据，早盘风控判断不可靠！\"\n            )\n            print(csv_data_stale_warning, file=sys.stderr)\n\n    live_payload = runtime_metrics[\"live_payload\"]"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100525,"output":705,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126107,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773993556957}}
