{"type":"message","id":"edb3e524","parentId":"ac81a906","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:01:43.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tester is now correctly catching both:\n1. `event_watch_mode_mismatch`: event_watch=cautious, runtime=halt - this is a legitimate design issue (two different data sources)\n2. `csv_index_data_stale`: CSV data is from 20260319 but today is 20260320 - our new check is working! ✅\n\nThe tester is now finding the CSV stale data issue. This is expected behavior since the CSV is indeed from yesterday.\n\nNow let me summarize the 4 layers of prevention I've added:\n\n1. **Layer 1**: `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` - Halt inheritance from previous day's last intraday recheck\n\n\n2. **Layer 2**: `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` - CSV data freshness warning (stderr print)\n3. **Layer 3**: `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` - CSV stale data explicit alert\n4. **Layer 4**: `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` - Prev halt → today buy-through detection\n\nThe previous day's halt-to-today buy-through check didn't trigger because my fix now prevents yesterday's halt from carrying forward, so today's orders correctly block buys.","thinkingSignature":"c31a189aa4f525ee675ffae9c66acd287d3487af2301d85b6332b7401157036b"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n四层防控全部生效，语法验证通过，Tester 运行正常。\n\n---\n\n## 新增防控机制（4 层）\n\n| 层 | 文件 | 机制 |\n|----|------|------|\n| **第一层** | `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` | 早盘继承上一交易日收盘 halt：`intraday_recheck_{T-1}_last → halt_new_buy=True` |\n| **第二层** | `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` | CSV 数据陈旧时直接 `stderr` 打印警告，防止 T-1 数据被误用 |\n| **第三层** | `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` | CSV 陈旧显式告警：`csv_index_data_stale` → HIGH |\n| **第四层** | `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` | 前日 halt + 今日有新增买 → `prev_halt_buy_through_{profile}` → CRITICAL |\n\n---\n\n**今天 Tester 捕获到的 2 个 WARN**：\n\n1. `event_watch_mode_mismatch`（HIGH）：event_watch=cautious / runtime=halt——这是双数据源设计差异，不影响实际风控\n2. `csv_index_data_stale`（HIGH）：**新增的第三层防控**——CSV 数据是 03/19，今日是 03/20，正确告警 ✅\n\n第四层（前日 halt → 今日买透）今天没有触发，因为 20260320 今天本身就被 halt 阻断了，没有新增买入。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99378,"output":565,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773993684759}}
