{"type":"message","id":"a167e213","parentId":"f1043d72","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:20:34.598Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a question about whether PTrade (迅投QMT/国泰海通 PTrade) can provide more stable real-time trading data. Let me think about what I know about PTrade.\n\nPTade is a professional quantitative trading terminal used in China A-shares. It connects to brokerage API and can provide:\n- Real-time market data (tick data, level 2 data)\n- Order placement/cancellation\n- Position updates\n- Account info\n\nKey considerations:\n1. PTrade is a full-service trading system, not just a data feed\n2. The user has PTrade open for \"ptrade实盘权限\" with 国泰海通\n\n\n3. PTrade's data comes directly from exchange feeds through the brokerage, so it's likely more reliable than third-party scraping solutions like THS or Tonghuashun\n4. I could potentially connect via HTTP APIs if PTrade exposes them, though the main integration method would be through its DLL/plugin interface rather than direct API calls\n5. Since PTrade data is typically served through a local client rather than a web API, I'd likely need to either read from local files/logs the client generates, or use IPC mechanisms to exchange data with the running PTrade process","thinkingSignature":"1f712a2f17040ad73147177410463c3e315bbc7ae553ca3ef921972b99e868dd"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n可以聊，但需要先了解几个现实情况再判断可行性：\n\n---\n\n**PTade 能提供的数据优势**\n\n- 直连券商柜台（国泰海通），行情源头是交易所推送，比爬虫/第三方软件更稳定、无漂移\n- 可拿到：**逐笔成交、level 2 买卖队列、实时持仓/资金变化**\n- 关键：**你自己的账户真实成交数据**——这比任何模拟撮合都准\n\n---\n\n**但有个实际问题**\n\nPTade 本身是 Windows 客户端，主要靠**迅投 API（DLL/QMT 接口）**或**本地文件/日志**与外部程序交互。没有开箱即用的 HTTP 接口。\n\n**可行的对接路径**：\n\n| 方案 | 难度 | 稳定性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| 迅投 QMT API（Python SDK）| 中 | ⭐⭐⭐ | 需在 Windows 上跑 QMT 客户端，对接后数据最准 |\n| PTade 本地文件/JSON 日志轮询 | 低 | ⭐⭐ | 部分券商 PTade 会落本地文件，定时读 |\n| 券商柜台 API（如国泰海通 REST API）| 高 | ⭐⭐⭐ | 大多数券商不对外开放，需要申请权限 |\n| 第三方行情聚合（文化/同花顺 L2）| 低 | ⭐⭐ | 付费数据，比爬虫稳 |\n\n---\n\n**我的建议**\n\n先确认一件事：你电脑上装的 PTade 是**国泰海通官方版**，还是通用迅投版？两个的接口开放程度不同。\n\n另外，你是想用 PTade 的数据**替代现有的 THS 实时行情**（更稳），还是想**接入真实成交记录**（打通红蓝两套盘）？\n\n两个方向不同，后者复杂度高很多，需要你配合测试。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85,"output":635,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":127098,"totalTokens":127818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773994802038}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b588ac9","parentId":"a167e213","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:21:06.087Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e479de80f0c34a360e3ecbea3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 16:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54e479de80f0c34a360e3ecbea3]\n张玲: 我装的是国泰海通官方版"}],"timestamp":1773994866083}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ec223aa","parentId":"1b588ac9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:21:30.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling confirmed she has the official Guotai Haian (国泰海通) version of PTrade installed. Let me think about what this means:\n\n1. 国泰海通 is a real brokerage - she has a real trading account with them\n2. PTrade is their version of the XunTou/XSpeed trading terminal\n3. The official version usually has specific API restrictions\n\nKey question: Can we access data from this?\n\nFor the Guotai Haian PTrade version:\n- They typically use the **国泰海通 ITchee API** or similar proprietary interface\n- Some official versions expose a **local HTTP service** on a specific port for quote data\n\n\n- The level of access really depends on what API permissions she's been granted through her PTRade authorization\n\nI should ask her directly whether she can access any development interfaces or API configurations within her PTrade terminal, since that'll tell us what we're working with.","thinkingSignature":"6abff6b5321d12c0855a20a1eba6259fe257b65cb15eab01c268f38ee8160dae"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n国泰海通官方版，那需要确认一件事：\n\n**你现在 PTrade 里有没有看到任何 API 接口或量化入口？**\n\n通常国泰海通官方版会有两种权限等级：\n\n- **普通客户端**：只能手动下单，没有 API 接口\n- **量化/专业版权限**：开通后会暴露 API 接口（通常是本地 HTTP 端口，如 `http://127.0.0.1:XXXX`）\n\n你登录 PTrade 后，帮我看一下：\n1. 顶部菜单有没有\"**量化**\"、\"**ITchee API**\"、\"**程序化交易**\"之类的入口？\n2. 或者\"**工具**\"菜单里有没有\"**接口设置**\"或\"**API 设置**\"？\n\n截个图或者告诉我有没有，我来帮你判断能否对接。\n\n---\n\n**如果确认有 API 权限**，国泰海通是可以拿到这些数据的：\n- 实时行情（5档/10档买卖盘）\n- 持仓、资金、当日成交\n- 推送式的实时回报（不用轮询）\n\n这对咱们现有系统的意义是：**用券商真实数据替代 THS 爬虫**，行情稳定性会大幅提升，而且能打通\"模拟盘 vs 实盘\"的精确对照。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85,"output":443,"cacheRead":24877,"cacheWrite":102266,"totalTokens":127671,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773994866086}}
