{"type":"message","id":"53766e34","parentId":"19469a74","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:44:16.022Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_54ncDWrHUcMRNGgCqgKfdBXc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: active_task_cli.py advance [-h] --path PATH [--status STATUS]\n                                  [--updated UPDATED] [--complete-current]\n                                  [--complete COMPLETE] [--current CURRENT]\n                                  [--promote-next] [--next NEXT]\n                                  [--append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED]\n                                  [--append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE]\n                                  [--set-blocker SET_BLOCKER]\n                                  [--clear-blockers]\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --path PATH           Path to ACTIVE_TASK.md\n  --status STATUS       New Status value\n  --updated UPDATED     Explicit Updated timestamp\n  --complete-current    Move existing Current item into Completed before other\n                        updates.\n  --complete COMPLETE   Compatibility alias: append the provided item to\n                        Completed.\n  --current CURRENT     Set the new Current item\n  --promote-next        Promote the first Next item into Current.\n  --next NEXT           Replace Next list; repeat for multiple items.\n  --append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED\n                        Append an item to Completed; repeat for multiple\n                        items.\n  --append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE\n                        Append an item to Evidence; repeat for multiple items.\n  --set-blocker SET_BLOCKER\n                        Replace Blockers with the provided item(s).\n  --clear-blockers      Clear Blockers."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":55,"aggregated":"usage: active_task_cli.py advance [-h] --path PATH [--status STATUS]\n                                  [--updated UPDATED] [-