{"type":"message","id":"845e820a","parentId":"53766e34","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:44:34.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Searching for data quality**\n\nI need to answer the user’s question effectively, likely by conducting a web search since they're asking about the data quality of the 国泰海通 ptrade client. I think I'll have to rely on both domain knowledge and some current pain points while checking official documents. If necessary, I can use either markdown-mirror-search or ddg-search for the web search. Let's see if I can confirm the stability of the data interface for PTrade.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ZrmnJ0jcv1H0kv5zMSNZMF4j","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"国泰海通 PTrade 官方版 数据 接口 稳定 行情 持仓 成交","count":5,"country":"CN","language":"zh","search_lang":"zh-hans","ui_lang":"zh-CN"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773996256025}}
